'''查理·肖恩·亞當斯'''（{{lang-en|Charlee Shaun Adams}}；{{bd|1995年|2月16日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是中場。他現在效力於[[英格蘭足球全國聯賽_(第一級)|英格蘭足球全國聯]]球隊[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|巴尼特]]。

==球員生涯==
亞當斯生於[[倫敦|倫敦]][[雷德布里奇區|雷德布里奇區]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.11v11.com/players/charlee-adams-241801/ |title=Charlee Adams |work=11v11.com |publisher=AFS Enterprises |accessdate=2 February 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619230608/https://www.11v11.com/players/charlee-adams-241801/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，年輕時曾在[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|西汉姆联]]試腳，但2011年夏天他與[[科尔特尼·豪塞|科尔特尼·豪塞]]前往[[伯明翰城足球俱樂部|伯明翰城]]<ref name=FAList1>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/~/media/Files/TheFAPortal/governance-docs/registrations/july-2011.ashx |title=List of Players Registered as Scholars in Accordance with Rule C.3 Between 01/07/2011 and 31/07/2011 |publisher=The Football Association |accessdate=10 January 2014 |archive-date=2013-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016070139/http://www.thefa.com/~/media/Files/TheFAPortal/governance-docs/registrations/july-2011.ashx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lfe.org.uk/blog/joining-the-blues-pre-season-part-1 |title=Joining The Blues: Pre-season Part 1 |author=Adams, Charlee |publisher=League Football Education |date=4 November 2011 |accessdate=10 January 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617140005/https://www.lfe.org.uk/blog/joining-the-blues-pre-season-part-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年5月，他與球會簽下一年職業合約，另加一年選擇權<ref name=TurnsPro>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/pro-deals-penned-828823.aspx |title=Pro deals penned |author=Walker, Andy |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=20 May 2013 |accessdate=10 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116141518/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/pro-deals-penned-828823.aspx |archivedate=2014年1月16日 }}</ref>。亞當斯在[[2013/14球季英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第三輪對[[布里斯托尔流浪者足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔流浪者]]賽事中入選為替補名單，在89分鐘以3-0領先時入替[[奥利弗·李|奥利弗·李]]<ref name=debut>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25663171 |title=Birmingham 3–0 Bristol Rovers |publisher=BBC Sport |date=14 January 2014 |accessdate=14 January 2014 |archive-date=2015-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031224656/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25663171 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年1月31日，他被外借到[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|全國聯]]球會[[林肯城足球俱乐部|林肯城]]至季末<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.redimps.co.uk/news/article/140131-charlee-adams-1331578.aspx |title=City snap up teenage midfielder |publisher=Lincoln City F.C |date=31 January 2014 |accessdate=31 January 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324114220/http://www.redimps.co.uk/news/article/140131-charlee-adams-1331578.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加盟後球隊便立刻成為先發陣容一員，首場比賽對[[夏利法斯鎮足球會|夏利法斯鎮]]踢足90分鐘並以3-1取勝。

2014/15球季未能成為伯明翰一線陣容後，再被外借回林肯城至2015年1月1日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.redimps.co.uk/news/article/141114-charlee-adams-2083302.aspx |title=Adams back on youth loan |publisher=Lincoln City F.C. |date=14 November 2014 |accessdate=14 November 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314181643/http://www.redimps.co.uk/news/article/141114-charlee-adams-2083302.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加盟後同樣地獲得不少上場機會，並在德比戰對[[格林斯比镇足球俱乐部|格林斯比镇]]取得職業生涯首顆進球，助球隊以3-1取勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lincolnshireecho.co.uk/Grimsby-Town-1-Lincoln-City-3-Charlie-Adams/story-25774756-detail/story.html |title=Grimsby Town 1 Lincoln City 3: Charlee Adams thunderbolt turns around derby thriller |author=Marshall, D. |newspaper=Lincolnshire Echo |date=28 December 2014 |accessdate=30 December 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141230124016/http://www.lincolnshireecho.co.uk/Grimsby-Town-1-Lincoln-City-3-Charlie-Adams/story-25774756-detail/story.html |dead-url=no }}<br>{{cite news |url=http://www.grimsbytelegraph.co.uk/WATCH-Lincoln-City-s-wonder-strike-helped-Grimsby/story-25777720-detail/story.html |title=WATCH: Lincoln City's wonder-strike that helped to down Grimsby Town |newspaper=Grimsby Telegraph |date=29 December 2014 |accessdate=30 December 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141230132738/http://www.grimsbytelegraph.co.uk/WATCH-Lincoln-City-s-wonder-strike-helped-Grimsby/story-25777720-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014年12月30日 }}</ref>。隨後他的租借期兩度延長至季末<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.redimps.co.uk/news/article/adams-extends-youth-loan-2159249.aspx |title=Adams extends youth loan |publisher=Lincoln City F.C |date=22 December 2014 |accessdate=30 December 2014 |archive-date=2016-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806213635/http://www.redimps.co.uk//news/article/adams-extends-youth-loan-2159249.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lincolnshireecho.co.uk/Lincoln-City-extend-loan-Birmingham-City-s/story-25901443-detail/story.html |title=Lincoln City extend loan of Birmingham City's Charlee Adams to the end of the season |author=Pakey, John |newspaper=Lincolnshire Echo |date=21 January 2015 |accessdate=26 January 2015 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402152436/http://www.lincolnshireecho.co.uk/Lincoln-City-extend-loan-Birmingham-City-s/story-25901443-detail/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年3月3日，替林肯城上場15次後被母會召回，教練[[加里·卢域|加里·卢域]]認為他在球隊U21比賽及跟一隊操練會成長得比較好<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/lincoln-city-birmingham-city-charlee-adams-2309698.aspx |title=Charlee Adams recalled from Lincoln |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=3 March 2015 |accessdate=3 March 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194519/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/lincoln-city-birmingham-city-charlee-adams-2309698.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季未他獲得一年新合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/charlee-adams-pens-new-deal-2444310.aspx |title=Charlee Adams pens new deal |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=6 May 2015 |accessdate=6 May 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305014333/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/charlee-adams-pens-new-deal-2444310.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年6月28日，亞當斯轉會[[英格蘭足球全國聯賽_(第一級)|英格蘭足球全國聯]]球隊[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|巴尼特]]，轉會費用未有公佈<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.barnetfc.com/news/2018/june/transfer--charlee-adams-signs-for-barnet-fc/ |title=Transfer {{!}} Charlee Adams signs for Barnet FC |access-date=2020-05-17 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125050405/https://www.barnetfc.com/news/2018/june/transfer--charlee-adams-signs-for-barnet-fc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

